rComments: Nice guy but I didn't learn much. You basically make videos on your own time with very little criteria, so you're just teaching yourself via practice. He just talked for the whole 4 hours, showing some videos, but boring. He was helpful to talk with after class but won't answer emails. He gave no grades all semester! and no feedback on big projects

1/4 of conversation was the MOST interesting video class ever. The other 3/4 of class conversation unfortunately boring. I really wish we would have had a say in the type of lectures. For example, one person knew and loved VDMX, no one else used it. Thus a 4 hour lecture on it is pointless if the one person already knows, and no one else needs it
